r></li><li>Flexible difficulty settings<br></li><li>Excessive gambling and alcohol consumption</li></ul><br>Remember, the house always wins!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239800/extras/255ebb2e684307a367914b80be845550.avif?t=1769185018\" width=616 height=347 /></span>",
